### Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/deltaapply.git
cd deltaapply

# Install dependencies
uv sync --dev

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Run tests with coverage
uv run pytest --cov=src/deltaapply --cov-report=html
```

